            <lg xml:id="TK569">
<l>ceruvanta pōḻtiṟ ciṟaiceyyā vēntaṉ </l>
<l> veruvantu veytu keṭum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The king who has not provided himself with a place of defence, will in times of war be seized with fear and quickly perish.</l>
            </lg>
